Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:54.33,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃机频频轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:56.72,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍将延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:00.61,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜烂的世界
